definitions.definition: A city , the state capital of Manipur , India .
A river that flows in the central plains of Manipur .
A valley that is flooded and drained by the Imphal river and its tributaries .
A former district, which consists of Imphal East and Imphal West.
A district that consists of areas that are in the eastern side of the Imphal River.
A district that consists of areas that are in the western side of the Imphal River.
A standard dialect of the official Meitei language, spoken in and around the state capital of Manipur .
A stealth guided missile destroyer warship of the Indian navy .

main_definition: A city , the state capital of Manipur , India .
secondary_definitions: A river that flows in the central plains of Manipur .
A valley that is flooded and drained by the Imphal river and its tributaries .
( Imphal District ) A former district, which consists of Imphal East and Imphal West.
( Imphal East ) A district that consists of areas that are in the eastern side of the Imphal River.
( Imphal West ) A district that consists of areas that are in the western side of the Imphal River.
A standard dialect of the official Meitei language, spoken in and around the state capital of Manipur .
( INS Imphal ) A stealth guided missile destroyer warship of the Indian navy .
